BATTLE ROYALE


This uses sk89q's WorldEdit plugin to allow a minecraft server to create an initial terrain which includes various objects for a special setting, such as a closed box for SMP action.  The javascript is run through this plugin with the help of Rhino's js.jar.



Place the script file into a folder named "craftscripts" in your main server folder.



Command in Minecraft to use:

/cs walls [players] <type>
[players] = number of players in the game
<type> = material type for the wall

Example: "/cs walls 3 bedrock"